   extrapolates wildly).  **drop_lift_i = mean residual of test set
   without anchor i  −  mean residual with all K anchors**.
   Per-anchor pass = drop ≥ τ=0.5 µm.
5. **Validation** (this notebook) compares anchors and the warped
   local CZ against `landmarks_qced` *inside the local bbox*.

**Headline.**  All subjects pass the drop-lift gate (min drop 2.4–4.6 µm)
but **anchors_correct ≤ 2/K** and **local recall@20 ≤ 0.07** on every
subject.  Internal consistency (drop-lift) is **not sufficient** for
